data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom, 3 full bath home with RELATED LIVING on MAIN LEVEL! The first floor in-law set-up is complete with a second kitchen, bedroom, living room w/French doors, and the first floor bath is full.  The main kitchen has granite counters galore and looks out to the park-like back yard.  The views are shared by a grand family room w/whitewashed brick fireplace and cathedral ceiling.  There are 4 more bedrooms + 2 full baths on the second level.  The oversized main bedroom has a door that opens up to a huge loft w/skylights that overlooks the family room.  The wood ceiling in the loft area offers a warm lodge experience, vacation at home!  Want more?  How about a finished basement area too! This home is located in sought after Brookridge Creek of Frankfort.  Just a hop, skip and a jump from Old Plank Trail and all that Frankfort has to offer, including award winning schools. The big ticket maintenance items have been addressed in recent years, such as a new roof in 2013, new furnace & A/C in 2013, kitchen remodel w/new stainless steel appliances in 2016, and the majority of windows were replaced 2018-2020.  Welcome home!
